2	 * Generates minimal VMD animation files for skinning visual regression.
3	 *
4	 * VMD binary layout:
5	 *   30 bytes  signature ("Vocaloid Motion Data 0002", null-padded)
6	 *   20 bytes  model name (Shift-JIS, null-padded; any value — not matched to PMX)
7	 *   4 bytes   bone frame count (i32 LE)
8	 *   per bone frame:
9	 *     15 bytes  bone name (Shift-JIS, null-padded)
10	 *      4 bytes  frame number (u32 LE)
11	 *     12 bytes  translation xyz (f32 × 3)
12	 *     16 bytes  rotation quaternion xyzw (f32 × 4)
13	 *     64 bytes  bezier interpolation (linear defaults: 20 20 107 107 pattern)
14	 *   4 bytes   morph frame count (i32 LE) = 0
15	 *   4 bytes   camera frame count (i32 LE) = 0
16	 *   4 bytes   light frame count (i32 LE) = 0
17	 *   4 bytes   self-shadow frame count (i32 LE) = 0
18	 *   4 bytes   property frame count (i32 LE) = 0
19	 */
20	
